        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository b6527741-a551-4d91-a423-fb8325801994).Image",
        "Description": "Good Day 47,\r\rI heard you&apos;ve received some new tools for your splendid efforts in earlier missions, Why not test them out?\r\rYour targets this time are the loners of the seaside down of Sapienza.\r\rA walking copyright infringement, Mario Saltatore has recently caught the ire of popular video game company Nintendon&apos;t, and they have contracted us to spare them a lwasuit.\r\rSolitary fisher Luciano Maino has made some clima activists very upset, and along with his hunting buddy Uberto needs to go.\r-D",
